select Count(0) as JumlahData from GL_JURNALH h (nolock) join GL_JURNALD d (nolock) on h.CO_ID=d.CO_ID and h.BR_ID=d.BR_ID and h.JOURNAL_NO=d.JOURNAL_NO left join OACT a (nolock) on a.AcctCode=d.ACCOUNT_NO left join OTRC b (nolock) on b.coid=h.CO_ID and b.TransCode=h.JOURNAL_ID left join OOCR c (nolock) on d.COST_CENTER = c.OcrCode where d.CO_ID= ':1' and h.BR_ID= ':2' and h.JOURNAL_DT between ':3' and ':4' AND D.JOURNAL_NO LIKE '%'+':5'+'%' AND ISNULL(h.REF_NO,'') like '%'+':6'+'%' and (d.COST_CENTER = ':7' OR COALESCE(':7','') = '') AND (d.ACCOUNT_NO = ':8' OR COALESCE(':8','') = '')
